 la gente", "speaker": null}, {"start": 86.78, "end": 88.4, "text": "si no hay taca de luz", "speaker": null}, {"start": 88.4, "end": 89.8, "text": "con crédito", "speaker": null}, {"start": 89.8, "end": 92.020004, "text": "no lo compras", "speaker": null}, {"start": 92.020004, "end": 94.42, "text": "entonces", "speaker": null}, {"start": 94.42, "end": 96.340004, "text": "para determinar la fin", "speaker": null}, {"start": 96.340004, "end": 97.58, "text": "la tipa que se tiene", "speaker": null}, {"start": 97.58, "end": 97.98, "text": "y", "speaker": null}, {"start": 97.98, "end": 102.66, "text": "va a ser la tasa de descuento", "speaker": null}, {"start": 102.66, "end": 104.44, "text": "capaz de igualar el valor", "speaker": null}, {"start": 104.44, "end": 105.92, "text": "de los recursos de la obra", "speaker": null}, {"start": 105.92, "end": 108.2, "text": "a valor de esa materia", "speaker": null}, {"start": 108.2, "end": 110.22, "text": "con el valor", "speaker": null}, {"start": 110.22, "end": 112.46, "text": "de los desembolsos", "speaker": null}, {"start": 112.46, "end": 114.22, "text": "a valor de ese valor.", "speaker": null}, {"start": 115.159996, "end": 115.799995, "text": "¿Qué quiere decir?", "speaker": null}, {"start": 115.94, "end": 117.7, "text": "Que tenemos que mover el dinero en el tiempo", "speaker": null}, {"start": 117.7, "end": 119.58, "text": "y una vez que lo tenemos,", "speaker": null}, {"start": 119.9, "end": 121.52, "text": "tenemos que encontrar la tasa", "speaker": null}, {"start": 121.52, "end": 123.979996, "text": "que es capaz de igualar a valor", "speaker": null}, {"start": 123.979996, "end": 124.7, "text": "del cero.", "speaker": null}, {"start": 125.7, "end": 127.18, "text": "Cada vez que calculemos el valor,", "speaker": null}, {"start": 127.7, "end": 131.44, "text": "vamos a estar buscando ese valor", "speaker": null}, {"start": 131.44, "end": 133.38, "text": "hasta que lo encontremos,", "speaker": null}, {"start": 133.52, "en